between for matrices and hyperSpec objects

between.Rd

Between is a shortcut function for x >= left & x <= right.

between(x, left, right)

# S4 method for matrix
between(x, left, right)

# S4 method for hyperSpec
between(x, left, right)

Arguments

x

matrix or hyperSpec object
left

Boundary values (must be scalars).
right

Boundary values (must be scalars).

Value

logical matrix indicating which elements of x are between left and right.

See also

dplyr::between()

Examples

between(flu [[]], 100, 400)
